channel.title: People are having trouble logging into my Server "Error_game_js5connect"
channel.description:
Alright guys,
So I finally have my server set up, hoping that I could have people log into it... However when my friend tried to log into it, it got stuck at Updating Server, and gave him an error message saying "Error_game_js5connect''. Now I know that this means that my server is not online, but on in my server box it says it is receiving the connection...
I'm not quite sure what is wrong. When I open up No-IP all of my IP's have smiling blushing faces beside them, which is what they are suppose to have. So everyone should be running fine...
If anyone could please help me out, please post below. I do have teamviewer if anybody thinks they can help that way too. Greatly appreciated :) Thanks!
